{"title": "dos2unix", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "dos2unix", "html": "<h1>dos2unix</h1>\n<h2>File Read</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">dos2unix -f -O /path/to/input-file</code></pre>\n<h2>File Write</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">dos2unix -f -n /path/to/input-file /path/to/output-file</code></pre>", "excerpt": "dos2unix File Read dos2unix -f -O /path/to/input-file File Write dos2unix -f -n /path/to/input-file /path/to/output-file", "tags": ["func:file-read", "func:file-write", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}